---
entity: Conversation
description: A customer-agent interaction within or linked to a support case.
provenance:
  author: support-ops
  source: domain-expert
  confidence: 0.88
  created: 2026-02-22
status: stable
---

## Attributes

occurred_at: datetime [required]
  | UTC timestamp for this interaction.

channel: enum [email, chat, call, ticket-comment]
  | Primary communication channel.

sentiment: enum [positive, neutral, negative]
  | Best-effort sentiment classification from conversation synthesis.

summary: text
  | Human-readable summary of interaction context and outcomes.

## Identity

A Conversation is identified by occurred_at and case context.

## Notes

Conversation summaries should preserve customer language for later taxonomy and rule refinement.
